claim-attack-on-norwegian-oil-tanker-en-route-to-israel-in-the-red-sea/0000018c-5d0e-d0ec-afbe-df2e167c0000</guid></item><item><title>图文视频和煽动：以色列国防军如何在 Telegram 上误导以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/graphic-videos-and-incitement-how-the-idf-is-misleading-israelis-on-telegram/0000018c-5ab5-df2f-adac-febd01c30000</link><description>负责心理战行动的以色列国防军部队运营着一个名为“72 Virgins – Uncensored”的 Telegram 频道，该频道针对当地观众提供“来自加沙地带的独家内容”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 04:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/graphic-videos-and-incitement-how-the-idf-is-misleading-israelis-on-telegram/0000018c-5ab5-df2f-adac-febd01c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政界人士就加沙战争做出了军方无法兑现的承诺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-are-making-promises-about-the-gaza-war-that-the-military-cant-keep/0000018c-5a93-d7d7-abce-7fd748430000</link><description>总参谋部对战斗的进展情况相当满意——尽管造成了损失——但没有迹象表明哈马斯即将崩溃 ■ 即使对 10 月 7 日失败负有责任的将军们辞职，他们也不能为内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-are-making-promises-about-the-gaza-war-that-the-military-cant-keep/0000018c-5a93-d7d7-abce-7fd748430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：自加沙地面行动开始以来，13名阵亡以色列士兵被误认为恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-live/report-hamas-israel-have-not-presented-new-cease-fire-proposal/0000018c-5bfc-db23-ad9f-7bfcc2020000</link><description>加沙火箭弹袭击特拉维夫，以色列中部城市一名男子被弹片炸伤 ■ 从黎巴嫩发射的火箭弹：两枚火箭弹被拦截，其余落在空旷地区，反坦克导弹击中梅图拉 ■ 美国对以色列在以色列使用白磷弹的报道感到担忧黎巴嫩 ■ 7 名以色列国防军士兵丧生，其中 6 名士兵在加沙战斗中丧生，1 名士兵死于军车事故 ■ 以色列国防军更新战争中受伤士兵人数为 1,645 名 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称 18,205 人死亡，49,645 人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 03:17:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-live/report-hamas-israel-have-not-presented-new-cease-fire-proposal/0000018c-5bfc-db23-ad9f-7bfcc2020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列检方命令警方调查休班士兵枪杀平民事件的调查处理情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prosecution-orders-police-to-probe-handling-of-kestelman-killing/0000018c-5af4-db23-ad9f-7afcb3880000</link><description>警方最初计划于本周提交调查结果，决定不对尤瓦尔·凯斯特曼进行尸检，尤瓦尔·凯斯特尔曼在耶路撒冷恐怖袭击现场被误认为是恐怖分子而被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prosecution-orders-police-to-probe-handling-of-kestelman-killing/0000018c-5af4-db23-ad9f-7afcb3880000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装用突破性的伊朗导弹威胁红海航运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthis-threaten-red-sea-shipping-with-groundbreaking-iranian-missile/0000018c-5aa4-df2f-adac-feadd7220000</link><description>弹道导弹旨在攻击城市和战略设施等固定目标。中国和伊朗更进一步，开发能够击中移动船只的弹道导弹。过去几周，胡塞武装两次向货轮发射此类炮弹</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 21:51:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthis-threaten-red-sea-shipping-with-groundbreaking-iranian-missile/0000018c-5aa4-df2f-adac-feadd7220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列现在应该知道：完美的胜利形象并不存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-should-know-by-now-the-perfect-victory-image-doesnt-exist/0000018c-5a32-db23-ad9f-7afa757e0000</link><description>试图通过血腥战争制造胜利形象是注定要失败的。即使有一张照片可以概括以色列对哈马斯的胜利，它也不太可能来自加沙废墟</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 20:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-should-know-by-now-the-perfect-victory-image-doesnt-exist/0000018c-5a32-db23-ad9f-7afa757e0000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质称加沙被囚禁是“俄罗斯轮盘赌”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/gaza-captivity-was-russian-roulette-freed-israeli-hostage-says/0000018c-59e7-d7d7-abce-7df7b3ac0000</link><description>莎朗·阿洛尼-库尼奥 (Sharon Alony-Cunio) 描述了她和她的双胞胎三岁孩子在加沙被哈马斯囚禁的时光，充满了恐惧和无力感。她说，现在，释放包括她丈夫大卫在内的剩余人质应该是以色列的首要任务</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 18:07:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/gaza-captivity-was-russian-roulette-freed-israeli-hostage-says/0000018c-59e7-d7d7-abce-7df7b3ac0000</guid></item><item><title>援助组织：加沙人在国外等待医疗救治时死亡，以色列军队行动迟缓</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/aid-group-israeli-army-dragging-its-feet-as-gazans-die-waiting-for-medical-care-abroad/0000018c-5970-db23-ad9f-79f81d0c0000</link><description>据哈马斯卫生部门称，约有 5 万名巴勒斯坦人在战争中受伤，但只有少数人得到及时救治。以色列非政府组织呼吁以色列军队加快允许加沙人在国外接受治疗的进程</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 17:42:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/aid-group-israeli-army-dragging-its-feet-as-gazans-die-waiting-for-medical-care-abroad/0000018c-5970-db23-ad9f-79f81d0c0000</guid></item><item><title>六名以色列国防军预备役军人在加沙战斗中丧生，军官死于车祸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/six-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-combat-in-gaza-another-dies-in-car-accident/0000018c-59d6-d6bd-a1ad-7bd6cd040000</link><description>七人中的五人在汗尤尼斯北部一所学校的爆炸中丧生，以色列军队正在调查为什么在部队进入之前该建筑没有遭到空中轰炸或炮火袭击</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 17:31:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/six-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-combat-in-gaza-another-dies-in-car-accident/0000018c-59d6-d6bd-a1ad-7bd6cd040000</guid></item><item><title>据报道以色列在黎巴嫩南部使用了美制白磷炸弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/israel-reportedly-used-u-s-made-white-phosphorus-bombs-in-southern-lebanon/0000018c-5957-df2f-adac-ff7fcbb80000</link><description>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，袭击中至少三人住院，四栋房屋被烧毁。以色列表示，该武器仅用于制造烟幕弹，而非用于进攻目的，而国际法禁止在平民地区使用该武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 15:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/israel-reportedly-used-u-s-made-white-phosphorus-bombs-in-southern-lebanon/0000018c-5957-df2f-adac-ff7fcbb80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国犹太人之间的裂痕翻开了新的危险篇章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-new-and-dangerous-chapter-in-the-rift-between-israeli-and-u-s-jews/0000018c-530e-df2f-adac-ff2f10750000</link><description>美国犹太作家对以色列的疏离感只是序幕。当前与加沙哈马斯的战争正在加剧他们与犹太复国主义本已复杂的关系</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 14:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-new-and-dangerous-chapter-in-the-rift-between-israeli-and-u-s-jews/0000018c-530e-df2f-adac-ff2f10750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列针对国际妇女团体的运动别有用心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-campaign-against-international-womens-groups-has-an-ulterior-motive/0000018c-5924-d7d7-abce-7df68c9f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 14:36:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-campaign-against-international-womens-groups-has-an-ulterior-motive/0000018c-5924-d7d7-abce-7df68c9f0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的困境：拯救你的生命就是被以色列驱逐</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/a-gazan-dilemma-when-saving-your-life-is-expulsion-by-israel/0000018c-58f0-df2f-adac-fefdc40a0000</link><description>逃离威胁加沙每个男人、女人和儿童生命的战争的愿望是否与爱国主义相矛盾？</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 13:27:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/a-gazan-dilemma-when-saving-your-life-is-expulsion-by-israel/0000018c-58f0-df2f-adac-fefdc40a0000</guid></item><item><title>在新的加沙范式中，埃及选择在战后战略中退居二线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/amid-a-new-gaza-paradigm-egypt-opts-to-take-a-back-seat-in-postwar-strategy/0000018c-586e-d6bd-a1ad-7bfe6d600000</link><description>在选举期间，埃及的塞西寻求加快一系列重要改革，以重振陷入经济危机的埃及经济。以色列和美国讨论的战后加沙计划可能会危及他的计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 13:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/amid-a-new-gaza-paradigm-egypt-opts-to-take-a-back-seat-in-postwar-strategy/0000018c-586e-d6bd-a1ad-7bfe6d600000</guid></item><item><title>他们被哈马斯俘虏，但他们最担心的是以色列的空袭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-were-held-captive-by-hamas-but-their-biggest-fear-was-israeli-airstrikes/0000018c-554b-db23-ad9f-7ddb3c990000</link><description>获释人质陈·戈尔茨坦-阿尔莫格和女儿阿加姆呼吁以色列努力释放仍被关押在加沙的140人，并透露人质遭到性侵犯：“此类袭击不仅仅发生在10月7日”</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 12:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-were-held-captive-by-hamas-but-their-biggest-fear-was-israeli-airstrikes/0000018c-554b-db23-ad9f-7ddb3c990000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲高级外长支持针对哈马斯的制裁计划；欧盟将讨论暴力以色列定居者禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-11/ty-article/top-europe-fms-back-sanctions-scheme-against-hamas-eu-to-talk-violent-israeli-settler-ban/0000018c-5899-db23-ad9f-78d917370000</link><description>欧盟三大国家法国、德国和意大利的外交部长在一封信中表示，欧盟必须打击“哈马斯”的基础设施和财政支持。在周一的会议上，欧盟外交部长还将讨论对约旦河西岸暴力事件负责的以色列定居者的旅行禁令</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 11:41:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-11/ty-article/top-europe-fms-back-sanctions-scheme-against-hamas-eu-to-talk-violent-israeli-settler-ban/0000018c-5899-db23-ad9f-78d917370000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，这位前途无量的以色列游泳运动员为救人而牺牲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/promising-israeli-swimmer-who-opted-for-combat-role-died-saving-many/0000018b-cdd0-d423-affb-fff37a740000</link><description>10 月 7 日，伊登·尼姆里 (Eden Nimri) 发现自己正在为自己以及纳哈奥兹军事哨所其他女兵的生命而战。她机智的反应救了 10 人，而她自己却被杀了</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 10:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/promising-israeli-swimmer-who-opted-for-combat-role-died-saving-many/0000018b-cdd0-d423-affb-fff37a740000</guid></item></channel></rss>